---
import "../styles/global.css";
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy - Xelleq";
const description = "Xelleq's privacy policy";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />

    <!-- Open Graph (for sharing on social media) -->
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <!-- Optional: <meta property="og:image" content="/social-preview.png" /> -->

    <!-- Twitter Card -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={title} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={description} />

    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../../public/favicon.ico" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navbar />
    <h1 class="page-title mt-4">Xelleq Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="container mt-4 mb-4">
        <p>Last updated: 04 August 2025</p>

        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>Xelleq</strong>. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use our services.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
        <p>
            We collect the following information when you create an account or use Xelleq:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, password, email address, and date of birth.</li>
            <li><strong>Profile Details:</strong> Profile image (optional) and profile description (optional).</li>
            <li><strong>User Content:</strong>
                Messages, posts, comments, replies, uploaded files (e.g., images, videos, documents, audio).
            </li>
            <li><strong>Voice Call Usage:</strong>
                We use a third-party service (Agora) to provide voice calling functionality.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Use of Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your data to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Provide and maintain our platform features.</li>
            <li>Personalize your experience.</li>
            <li>Enable real-time communication (voice, chat, etc.).</li>
            <li>Moderate content and maintain a safe environment.</li>
            <li>Communicate updates or changes to policies.</li>
            <li>Improve our services over time.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Your data is stored securely on our servers.</li>
            <li>Passwords are encrypted.</li>
            <li>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information.</li>
            <li>Despite our best efforts, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
        <p>
            We do not sell or rent your personal information.
            We may share data with:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Agora – for enabling voice calls (see their
                <a href="https://www.agora.io/en/terms-of-service/" target="_blank">terms of service</a>).
            </li>
            <li>Legal authorities – if required by law or to enforce our policies.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p>
            Xelleq is intended for users aged 13 and older.
            We collect date of birth during registration to help enforce this.
            We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access or update your profile information at any time.</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your account and associated data.</li>
            <li>Contact us with privacy-related concerns.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active.
        Deleted accounts and content are purged within a reasonable timeframe unless retention is required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy as our services evolve.
            We will notify you of major changes via email.
            Your continued use of Xelleq implies your acceptance of the updated policy.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
            If you have questions or concerns about your privacy, please contact <strong>support@xelleq.com</strong>.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for using Xelleq. Made with Love.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
